Well-known actor Menzi Ngubane threw his father a huge birthday party this past weekend. He said in a heartfelt message that he considers himself a son to him and still run to him for advice. "He’s the strongest human being I’ve ever known, knowledgeable & I’m humbled to experience and learn from his wisdom. "This past weekend marked the most important celebration in my life. My dad turned 90yrs & my Queen and I decided to bring family & friends together to honour our most cherished gentleman, my dad. I feel very blessed to have him in my life, as much as I’m a father myself," said the former Generations and Isibaya actor.    